reviews.customers_say: Customers find the sweater well-made, soft, and comfortable, with one noting it doesn't itch. Customers like the color, with one describing it as a rich jewel tone, and find the material luxurious.

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very well-made, quality material, soft and comfy
items.body: Such a beautiful evergreen color! I absolutely love it. This sweater is soft, well-made and looks quality.!!! It’s a great weight to wear a blouse or T-shirt under for fall and winter. Again, I was taken back by the quality of the material and how well it was made. Read more
items.author: SFoster

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars My go to sweater!
items.body: Arach& Cloz always delivers very good quality and comfort. I have seven of tgese sweaters in different colors and styles. The fit is true to size, great color selections. The wool blend is so soft and delivers great quality wash after wash! Read more
items.author: Customer

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great basic sweater
items.body: So cute. Color is true, material is nice and soft, and has held up after a couple washes. It's true to size as well. Will buy in other colors. Read more
items.author: Susitna Soho

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars Fabric and size change
items.body: I recently lost 20 lbs and had to get some new clothes . I purchased several sweaters from this brand- initially they were beautiful- great purchase- classic style- beautiful soft fabric - real wow factor. Recently their fabric is rougher and sizing smaller. I am planning to return a couple sweaters because the size small is now too small and the fabric is dull. My intial purchases tho- i love. (I dd get one of their striped sweaters recently- beautiful quality). Will probably steer clear of their newer fabric if i can. Read more
items.author: Sunny

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Soft Sweater & Stylish But Scratchy Tag Be Gone!
items.body: Finally, a V-neck sweater that doesn’t make me look like I raided the closet of someone six inches taller. The arms are actually the right length (petites, you know the struggle), and the fabric is so soft I’ve caught myself stroking it like a Bond villain with a cat. The blue is exactly as promised online—no shady color surprises. I’m 5’2” and 185 apple shape and got the XL. Fits great without showing the tummy roll. Now, the tag. Whoever designed it clearly skipped the ‘comfort matters’ memo. Scratchy, annoying, and destined for the scissors. Once that’s gone, we’re golden. Fingers crossed it survives the wash without pilling, but for now, it’s a solid win: true to size, cozy, and stylish. Read more
items.author: Dlea

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice sweater
items.body: Soft, comfortable, and soft. Lovely color. Read more
items.author: Gloria Peterson

items.title: 3.0 out of 5 stars You may get the wrong size.
items.body: The sweaters are beautiful, good quality nice colors. I ordered two size medium, one was a true medium and the other was a true small but stated medium . I can still wear the smaller one but really wanted a medium size. This was a manufactured defect because tags both say medium. Read more
items.author: donna avery

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great fit, style, softness
items.body: Love this sweater. Soft, lightweight but not thin. Washes well. Buying more Read more
items.author: LV

short_description:
Womens Dress is made for a polished look that still feels comfortable to wear. It is designed to sit cleanly on the body with a flattering shape that works for day plans and dressier moments without feeling overdone.

The fit focuses on balance rather than extremes, so you can move naturally while still getting a defined silhouette. Choose your usual size for a closer look, or size up if you prefer a little more ease through the waist and hips.

Styling is simple: keep accessories minimal for a clean finish, or add a jacket and statement shoes when you want a sharper outfit. This piece photographs well thanks to smooth lines and a structured feel that stays put once you have it adjusted.

With the right fit and simple styling, this item becomes an easy go-to when you want something that looks intentional without requiring extra effort.

To keep it looking sharp, follow the care label first and avoid high heat when drying or steaming if the material is sensitive.

If you are between sizes, choose based on how close you like the fit through the waist and hips, then adjust with your usual layering choices.

long_description:
Womens Dress is a versatile piece you can reach for when you want a put-together look that still feels comfortable. The goal is simple: a silhouette that reads polished, photographs well, and stays wearable for a full day or a long night.

Fit and sizing Fit is where most outfits win or lose. This design aims for a balanced shape with a defined line through the torso, a clean waist, and a smooth finish through the hips and legs. If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up; if you like a closer fit, stay true to size. Sizes may include: One Size.

Fabric and comfort Comfort is not just about softness. It is also about movement and how the fabric behaves as you walk, sit, and stand. A fabric blend with a bit of give helps it keep its shape while still feeling wearable.

Highlights A clean neckline and a refined silhouette for an elevated look. Designed to layer easily with jackets, wraps, or sweaters. Works well with both minimal accessories and statement pieces.

How to style Styling ideas: keep it minimal with neutral shoes and one standout accessory. For a relaxed daytime look, add a denim jacket or cardigan. For events, switch to a bolder shoe and a small clutch for a sharper finish.

Color notes Available colors may include: B-grey, Cable-camel, Olive Green, B-black, Rose, B-navy, B-khaki, Rose Red, Cable-coffee, B-dark Blue, Lake Blue, Cable-green, Cable-dark Blue, Purple. If a shade is sold out, check back as availability can change.

Care Care guidance matters if you want it to keep its shape and finish. Follow the label first.
